OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Menopause leave' trial    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frejected by government     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers have rejected a proposal from
OL,6, MPs to introduce "menopause leave"     
OL,7, pilots in England, arguing it could be 
OL,8, "counterproductive".                   
OL,10,FIt also dismissed a recommendation to  
OL,11,Fmake menopause a protected             
OL,12,Fcharacteristic under the Equality Act. 
OL,14,FThe suggestions came from the Women and
OL,15,FEqualities Committee, which accused    
OL,16,Fministers of making "glacial progress" 
OL,17,Fon menopause support.                  
OL,19,FThe government insisted it had an      
OL,20,F"ambitious" plan to improve help.      
